****************************************************************
The Department of Heath is still applying perifocal vector control measures
including insecticide spraying and reduction of mosquito breeding sites.
The cool season, which started mid-May and is less favorable to the
mosquito population, probably plays a role in the decrease of the weekly
number of cases.
